flowchart TD
A[Incoming Call] --> B["Greeting: Thank you for calling Pop A Lock. How can I help you today?"]
B --> C[Confirm and repeat callback number]
C --> D[Collect first and last name]
D --> E[Collect service street address]
E --> F{Customer knows address?}
F -->|Yes| G[Double click service area from dropdown]
F -->|At business, unknown address| H[Use Google to locate correct address]
F -->|Refuses address| I["Select Augusta sub area<br/>Type: customer refused address<br/>Click GPS<br/>Select No<br/>Quote Augusta Main base price<br/>Explain price may increase"]
G --> J["Click magnifying glass<br/>Verify address and assign zone"]
H --> J
I --> J
J --> K{Home or business?}
K -->|Home| L[Continue]
K -->|Business| M["Collect business name<br/>Add to call"]
L --> N[Confirm service type]
M --> N
N --> O{Service requested?}
O -->|Auto lockout| P[Auto lockout flow]
O -->|Home| Z1[Home service branch]
O -->|Business| Z2[Business service branch]
P --> Q["Ask: is anyone trapped inside vehicle?"]
Q --> R{Child trapped?}
R -->|Yes| S["Select car door unlocking<br/>Go to Discounts tab<br/>Select EDU<br/>Confirm price equals 0<br/>Add call<br/>Notify management immediately"]
R -->|No| T[Continue standard auto lockout]
T --> U[Add vehicle year]
U --> V[Select manufacturer from dropdown]
V --> W[Select model from dropdown]
W --> X[Add vehicle color]
X --> Y[Ask key location]
Y --> Y1{Keys in trunk?}
Y1 -->|Yes| Y2["Select trunk<br/>Inform: we guarantee cabin access only<br/>Trunk access may require extra service"]
Y1 -->|Cabin| Y3[Select cabin]
Y2 --> AA[Quote total price and ETA]
Y3 --> AA
AA --> AB["Inform: tech will call or text when on the way"]
AB --> AC[Request driver license ready]
AC --> AD["Confirm payment methods: cash, card, Cash App"]
AD --> AE["Ask for locating details<br/>Gate code, parking row, clothing, landmarks"]
AE --> AF[Proceed to closing]
AF --> AG[Repeat full service summary]
AG --> AH["Ask: how did you hear about us?"]
AH --> AI[Click Add Call]
AI --> AJ[Leave lead status equals NONE]
AJ --> AK[Do not assign]
AK --> AL[Do not schedule]
AL --> AM[End call]
AA --> PF{Customer hesitates on price?}
PF -->|Military| PF1[Offer 10 percent military discount with valid ID]
PF -->|General hesitation| PF2[May reduce up to 10 dollars to secure booking]
PF -->|Needs more than 10| PF3[Escalate to management]
PF1 --> AB
PF2 --> AB
PF3 --> AB
